## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all possible scenarios of ethical dilemmas faced by managers. Additionally, the perspectives provided are primarily from Western business contexts, which may not fully apply to different cultural or organizational settings. Further research could explore a broader range of industries and cultural influences on managerial ethics.

